    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get focusing on impact. but sometimes the behavior is just... erratic. like they're behaving in a way that feels almost malicious or just totally chaotic, like they're intentionally trying to mess things up for others. is there a professional way to capture that kind of \"troublemaking\" energy without sounding like i'm just venting?",
